g.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQBZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=4b6698fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"9f0335d025f55dc98411cf4bc5af43ea39190bae","tid":1727342,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78d6c194347439f6396cd01a06a71f4af77ec39","tid":1727342,"uid":3747,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:15:14.000Z","msg":"名字沒有去問 只求共我放任 星光裡飛車去<br />\n祈望我倆佔有這黑夜 踏上這架快車"},{"pid":"f84fdb83b565a0a107b3842544bfb5c746b0fb41","tid":1727342,"uid":35598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:17:42.000Z","msg":"十個決定去救火的少年～"},{"pid":"5b33a4e7fc3d7ca721f32086bb904f301f353842","tid":1727342,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:19:07.000Z","msg":"在這社會最怕走得太前<br />\n罷了罷了 便歸家往後轉"},{"pid":"e69a820fa1a93e27e7cb40cb725641b447948c57","tid":1727342,"uid":40743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5316b17f9b99ea6c421ccbd7b149fed29af2608","tid":1727342,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"022a2a334c20df70d6ff31aee864730dc1e9075e","tid":1727342,"uid":79562,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d64fac51f719d0b277766a3d196d95d08c7509d3","tid":1727342,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9280303ed9fc4001fecae7af64439da40fcff35f","tid":1727342,"uid":23140,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"cited